### Access Control

Zone access is controlled through the role hierarchy configured in the Role & Access Control task:
- **ADMIN/CREATE roles**: Access to all zones
- **WRITE role**: Access to curated and consumption zones
- **READ role**: Access to consumption zone only

Adjust privileges in the Grant Role Privileges step based on your specific requirements.